				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'd go for that.
<br />

<br />
Change the Fire pet into a "group enhancement" familiar. Have him toss a set 3 tick (short buff-box) group targeted song-like spells. A 20pt heal & 10pt mana heal once every 18 seconds, a 3 tick bard-song-like 10% dd focus and a 3 tick +10% instant heal focus.
<br />

<br />
He'd alternate them so you'd have 3 "songs" active. If you have a bard in the group the only effect that would be useful would be the unique 10% heal focus, so on raids having a mage in a healer heavy group would be recommended.<br />_________________<br />Aquilistor Portavendor
